<storybody><![CDATA[<p>E-commerce giant Amazon is receiving flak from social media users after it was found that door mats with Hindu gods and goddesses on them were being sold on its website.</p><p>Social media users took their anger to both Twitter and Facebook and since then #BoycottAmazon has been trending on the social networking sites.</p><p>&nbsp; <br /></p><p><br /></p><blockquote data-twitter-extracted-i1465126106014586125="true" class="twitter-tweet" data-lang="en"><p dir="ltr" lang="en">I uninstalled <a href="https://twitter.com/amazonIN" mce_href="https://twitter.com/amazonIN">@amazonIN</a> for Insulting Hindus by selling range of Hindu God and Goddess Doormats. <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/BoycottAmazon?src=hash" mce_href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/BoycottAmazon?src=hash">#BoycottAmazon</a> <a href="https://t.co/CGUoNqJcLK" mce_href="https://t.co/CGUoNqJcLK">pic.twitter.com/CGUoNqJcLK</a></p>�?? sunil kapoor (@sunilkapoor8) <a href="https://twitter.com/sunilkapoor8/status/739341172171243520" mce_href="https://twitter.com/sunilkapoor8/status/739341172171243520">June 5, 2016</a></blockquote> <script async="" src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" mce_src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script><br /><blockquote data-twitter-extracted-i1465126106014586125="true" class="twitter-tweet" data-lang="en"><p dir="ltr" lang="en">WTF! Amazon Is Selling Doormats With Hindu Goddess &amp; Holy Quran's Pic On It. <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/BoycottAmazon?src=hash">#BoycottAmazon</a><br />RT &amp; Spread! <a href="https://t.co/t38aqZIfbr">pic.twitter.com/t38aqZIfbr</a></p>�?? Sir Ravindra Jadeja (@SirJadeja) <a href="https://twitter.com/SirJadeja/status/739339227696115712">June 5, 2016</a></blockquote> <script async="" src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script><br /><blockquote data-twitter-extracted-i1465126106014586125="true" class="twitter-tweet" data-lang="en"><p dir="ltr" lang="en">Just because we are tolerant community, no one give you permission to intolerant with our sentiment <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/BoycottAmazon?src=hash">#BoycottAmazon</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/amazon">@Amazon</a></p>�?? हर�?श (@TheBigMochad) <a href="https://twitter.com/TheBigMochad/status/739303907990474752">June 5, 2016</a></blockquote> <script async="" src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script><br /><blockquote data-twitter-extracted-i1465126106014586125="true" class="twitter-tweet" data-lang="en"><p dir="ltr" lang="en"><a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/BoycottAmazon?src=hash">#BoycottAmazon</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/amazon">@amazon</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/AmazonHelp">@AmazonHelp</a> <br />STOP abusing Hindu Deities <br />Enough is Enough<br />REMOVE these products <a href="https://t.co/qCm4NOZnFb">pic.twitter.com/qCm4NOZnFb</a></p>�?? No Conversion (@noconversion) <a href="https://twitter.com/noconversion/status/739278740413255683">June 5, 2016</a></blockquote><p> <script async="" src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script><br />But this was not it, retailers on Amazon were also selling <b>Islamic themed and Jesus Christ doormats. </b>This has infuriated many and people have been posting about uninstalling the Amazon mobile app. </p><p><br<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-lang="en"></br<blockquote></p><p dir="ltr" lang="en">Not only <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/hindureligion?src=hash">#hindureligion</a> amazon your seller desrescpet our <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/Kabasharif?src=hash">#Kabasharif</a> n <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/Profetmohammad?src=hash">#Profetmohammad</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/BoycottAmazon?src=hash">#BoycottAmazon</a> <a href="https://t.co/1SAyd0WvmD">pic.twitter.com/1SAyd0WvmD</a></p>�?? Semi (@Lovesemi5) <a href="https://twitter.com/Lovesemi5/status/739212799012831233">June 4, 2016</a> <script async="" src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script><p>&nbsp;</p><p>However, Amazon is a<b> platform for retailers to sell their products </b>and has different websites for various countries. Many have criticised this 'fiasco' by Amazon but a few did react differently.&nbsp; </p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><br /></p><blockquote data-twitter-extracted-i1465126106014586125="true" class="twitter-tweet" data-lang="en"><p dir="ltr" lang="en">Childish trend, <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/BoycottAmazon?src=hash">#BoycottAmazon</a>. Why just doormat, put gods on toilet paper, condoms. Our tradition, Hinduness too big to be belittled by it</p>�?? Abhijit Majumder (@abhijitmajumder) <a href="https://twitter.com/abhijitmajumder/status/739186766159220737">June 4, 2016</a></blockquote> <script async="" src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script><br /><blockquote data-twitter-extracted-i1465126106014586125="true" class="twitter-tweet" data-lang="en"><p dir="ltr" lang="en">Indians are so eager to <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/BoycottAmazon?src=hash">#BoycottAmazon</a> for putting Goddess pictures on doormats but everyday news of Indian women being raped has no effect.</p>�?? Priyanka (@autumnrainwish) <a href="https://twitter.com/autumnrainwish/status/739282915993886720">June 5, 2016</a></blockquote> <script async="" src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script><br /><blockquote data-twitter-extracted-i1465126106014586125="true" class="twitter-tweet" data-lang="en"><p dir="ltr" lang="en">After seeing <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/BoycottAmazon?src=hash">#BoycottAmazon</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/amazonIN">@amazonIN</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/Flipkart">@Flipkart</a> and <a href="https://twitter.com/snapdeal">@snapdeal</a> s office employees and owners reaction. �??? <a href="https://t.co/KcxHsjr1k3">pic.twitter.com/KcxHsjr1k3</a></p>�?? Dr.Jay �?? (@VegGujju) <a href="https://twitter.com/VegGujju/status/739194435179712512">June 4, 2016</a></blockquote>
<script async="" src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script>After the social media outrage, Amazon has removed these products from its website.&nbsp; <p>&nbsp;</p>]]></storybody>
